description: For sale: $125,000. Turnkey 2 bedroom cabin on large wooded lot with over 100' of lakeshore, so close you can almost touch the water from your large wrap-around deck overlooking Long Lake. Beautiful views of sunrises and sunsets from the shore. Wood burning fireplace to cozy up to in the evening . 2 sheds and ample parking on lot.  2 hours north of the Twin Cities off I35 and 30 minutes SW of Duluth makes this summer retreat easy access from all areas.   Quiet 60 acre spring feed lake with abundant wildlife including loons, deer, trumpeter swans, eagles and migrating water fowl to enjoy from the screen room on the deck. The cabin is offered fully furnished with updated appliances and comfy living space. Close on this property in the morning and enjoy dinner off the grill the same evening after a refreshing swim in the lake.
